South Africa’s Postbank to Apply for Bank License by Year-End, Beeld Says

-- B y   R o b e r t   B r a n d
-- 
2011-08-30T05:23:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-30/south-africa-s-postbank-to-apply-for-bank-license-by-year-end-beeld-says.html
South Africa ’s Postbank will apply
for a banking license in December, Beeld reported, citing Roy
Padayachie, the minister of communications.  Postbank, a unit of the South African Post Office, plans to
trade as a retail bank, the newspaper cited Padayachie as
saying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
